# Authored presentation assets

Version 8.3 ships optimized glTF/GLB presentation models for the six priority weapons:

- `pulse_pistol.glb`
- `vector_rifle_mk2.glb`
- `scatter_cannon.glb`
- `longshot_mk2.glb`
- `arc_blade_mk2.glb`
- `void_reaper.glb`

Each model uses named mechanical nodes such as `magazine`, `slide`, `bolt`, `pump`, `energyCell`, `heatVent_*`, and `bladeSegment_*`. The first-person presentation system animates those nodes during firing, reloading, heat buildup, and melee attacks. Procedural modular models remain available as a complete fallback if GLB loading fails.
